  ('9486c7b3-8f4d-5feb-b4c3-a7b137b23b1a', 'Nutella Mocha', 'A Nutella Mocha is a decadent blend of rich espresso, velvety steamed milk, Nutella Spread, topped with a silky layer of foam for a perfect balance of sweetness and depth. Note: Please be aware that micro-foam may not retain its texture as effectively during transit in a sealed takeaway cup. The delicate foam, created by incorporating air, can gradually dissipate over time.', 'Coffee', 'Hot', true, true, 130),
